## Development Setup

For contributors and advanced users:

```bash
# Clone and install in development mode
git clone https://github.com/nabla-ml/nb.git
cd nabla
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest

# Format and lint code
ruff format nabla/
ruff check nabla/ --fix
```

